1
00:00:58,016 --> 00:01:00,992
=Within The Grip=

2
00:01:00,992 --> 00:01:02,962
=Episode 22=

3
00:01:03,898 --> 00:01:06,938
(The Real and the Fake Zhaoxi)

4
00:01:07,130 --> 00:01:09,562
(Fufeng Pavilion)

5
00:01:11,200 --> 00:01:14,680
He sent me away,
so he could pin everything on me.

6
00:01:15,359 --> 00:01:18,959
What a shame I couldn't witness
him reap what he sowed.

7
00:01:20,640 --> 00:01:23,719
We're all family.
Save the snide remarks.

8
00:01:24,640 --> 00:01:26,599
Now, you remember we're family?

9
00:01:26,879 --> 00:01:28,560
When you hired
the killer to kill Zhaoxi,

10
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:30,280
did family bonds ever cross your mind?

11
00:01:30,280 --> 00:01:31,359
- You...
- Enough.

12
00:01:32,079 --> 00:01:32,799
Who would believe

13
00:01:33,120 --> 00:01:35,040
a eunuch could be so audacious

14
00:01:35,599 --> 00:01:39,040
and repeatedly forge imperial edicts
to frame loyal subjects?

15
00:01:40,200 --> 00:01:41,560
Now, he's hanged himself.

16
00:01:42,560 --> 00:01:45,719
The mastermind behind this
may never surface.

17
00:01:51,599 --> 00:01:54,879
No need for that look. Speak plainly.

18
00:01:57,519 --> 00:01:58,879
So who exactly are you?

19
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:01,200
You're...

20
00:02:02,519 --> 00:02:03,239
disguised?

21
00:02:05,319 --> 00:02:09,240
I'm here at General Shen's request
to help you root out internal threats.

22
00:02:10,159 --> 00:02:12,599
What are your plans
given the current situation?

23
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:14,960
Shall I lend a hand?

24
00:02:16,479 --> 00:02:19,199
The situation is delicate. Since...

25
00:02:21,879 --> 00:02:24,439
Since you know our family
harbors no treasonous intentions,

26
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:26,560
we hope you'll vouch for us.

27
00:02:27,759 --> 00:02:30,680
But these are internal family matters.

28
00:02:31,159 --> 00:02:32,479
We'll handle them ourselves.

29
00:02:36,599 --> 00:02:37,199
Yuluo.

30
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:46,879
I've been thinking since last night.

31
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:48,840
In the past,

32
00:02:49,120 --> 00:02:51,520
I obsessed over
winning Father's approval,

33
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:54,176
and neglected all familial bonds
within these walls.

34
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:56,479
I thought

35
00:02:57,039 --> 00:03:00,719
that among my siblings,
Wenshuang was closest to me.

36
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:03,319
I didn't expect...

37
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:08,240
You were right.

38
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:10,719
Our family is now everyone's target.

39
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:13,000
Father's health worsens daily.

40
00:03:13,639 --> 00:03:14,960
Both Zhaoxi and Wenshuang are...

41
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,960
My past perspective was too narrow.

42
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:24,759
After all this, I want
to liquidate our assets,

43
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:26,639
keep only what's in Jiangnan,

44
00:03:27,639 --> 00:03:29,400
and take everyone far from this turmoil.

45
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:32,080
Do you really think

46
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:36,000
that moving south would
let the family escape unscathed?

47
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:38,919
But now, Wenshuang
and Chief He are dead.

48
00:03:39,039 --> 00:03:40,439
How do we find the mastermind?

49
00:03:41,439 --> 00:03:42,960
Aren't we all in mortal danger

50
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:45,360
until we uncover them?

51
00:03:47,599 --> 00:03:49,000
Do you remember

52
00:03:49,879 --> 00:03:51,759
those hunters below the Yunya Temple?

53
00:03:53,319 --> 00:03:57,000
When the temple collapsed in a storm,
merchants flocked to donate.

54
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:59,120
But that same storm

55
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:01,919
also affected the hunters
at the mountain's foot.

56
00:04:02,719 --> 00:04:05,360
Some knew their plight,
while others didn't.

57
00:04:05,919 --> 00:04:10,599
But only you brought them grain
and repaired their homes.

58
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:15,080
Charity for the temple is noble,
but so is aiding the hunters.

59
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:19,120
The difference? The former
brought social prestige.

60
00:04:19,759 --> 00:04:22,079
The latter came purely from compassion.

61
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:26,279
That's when my opinion
of you began to change.

62
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:29,959
I'm an outsider to the Gu family,

63
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:32,560
but you're smart, Chaosheng.

64
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:35,839
You must realize
once caught in this storm,

65
00:04:36,279 --> 00:04:37,800
complete escape is impossible.

66
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:40,879
If the Gu family withdraws,

67
00:04:41,079 --> 00:04:44,279
the truth may never surface.

68
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:48,000
More will suffer in the future.

69
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:50,720
Is that what you want?

70
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:54,600
But since the schemer covets
the Gu family and Xuanji Pavilion,

71
00:04:55,519 --> 00:04:57,319
let's set a trap

72
00:04:57,879 --> 00:05:00,079
and end this here.

73
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:06,720
It strikes me now
that staying in our family,

74
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:10,480
no, even the Xuanji Pavilion,

75
00:05:10,879 --> 00:05:14,279
doesn't showcase your talents
but buries them.

76
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:19,360
I once thought your name
meant stunning beauty,

77
00:05:19,959 --> 00:05:22,000
but now, I see it's from the poem,

78
00:05:22,839 --> 00:05:26,680
"Night winds rise, the fish leap;
Crossing the banks to watch the flow."

79
00:05:28,199 --> 00:05:32,759
Your brilliance proves
you're never meant for a shallow pond.

80
00:05:33,338 --> 00:05:36,090
(Vast Mind, Eternal Will)

81
00:05:51,439 --> 00:05:53,680
Can he truly be trusted?

82
00:05:54,759 --> 00:05:56,920
What if he's the mastermind?

83
00:05:57,720 --> 00:06:01,399
Whoever drove Chief He to suicide

84
00:06:02,199 --> 00:06:03,560
must hold immense power.

85
00:06:03,879 --> 00:06:06,759
I have my suspicions.

86
00:06:07,319 --> 00:06:07,920
Who?

87
00:06:08,519 --> 00:06:13,120
The mastermind knows the Gu family well.

88
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:16,720
They must have direct connections.

89
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:21,160
And many unanswered questions remain.

90
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:26,680
You said the physician
who examined Zhaoxi

91
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:30,519
was found by you casually
after catching a cold at the theater.

92
00:06:33,439 --> 00:06:37,079
Were you alone at the theater that day?

93
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:39,040
The theater...

94
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:42,680
I was with...

95
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:04,079
It seems you already have someone
in mind for the mastermind.

96
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:07,279
And you?

97
00:07:09,560 --> 00:07:10,680
Tomorrow's wedding...

98
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:13,519
The wedding will proceed as planned.

99
00:07:19,279 --> 00:07:21,040
Did it never occur to you

100
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:23,399
that I might be the mastermind?

101
00:07:34,959 --> 00:07:36,120
Of course I suspected you.

102
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:40,519
But your life-risking rescues

103
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:41,839
are etched in my memory.

104
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:45,360
I didn't want to say this,

105
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:50,040
but Xuan Qing's death made me realize

106
00:07:51,079 --> 00:07:53,240
some words, some things,

107
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:57,199
once missed, bring endless regret.

108
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:29,720
Long ago, I thought
when Zhaoxi took a wife,

109
00:08:29,839 --> 00:08:32,384
I'd surely have wedding robes tailored
for him and his wife.

110
00:08:32,989 --> 00:08:36,039
Pity he didn't get to wear it.

111
00:08:36,919 --> 00:08:40,279
Even you can't wear it
with your beloved.

112
00:08:43,600 --> 00:08:44,960
This wedding robe is beautiful.

113
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:47,480
I'm glad you like it.

114
00:09:17,402 --> 00:09:19,418
(Happiness)

115
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:48,559
Chaosheng.

116
00:10:19,240 --> 00:10:20,200
Have you decided?

117
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:24,559
Once you step through this door,
there's no turning back.

118
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:29,399
You and the entire Gu family
are worried about the people,

119
00:10:29,919 --> 00:10:31,799
and you've given up
the chance to walk away.

120
00:10:32,799 --> 00:10:34,720
How could I shrink back?

121
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:43,159
It is we who should thank you.

122
00:10:44,679 --> 00:10:47,639
The Xuanji Pavilion and our family
are lucky to have you.

123
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:52,279
Later, our family and the Pavilion
will surely protect you

124
00:10:53,840 --> 00:10:55,279
with all we've got.

125
00:10:58,720 --> 00:11:01,080
Thank you, Chaosheng.

126
00:11:01,279 --> 00:11:04,759
Alright, it's getting late.
Don't keep the groom waiting.

127
00:11:27,546 --> 00:11:32,609
♪Willows sway in the twilight breeze♪

128
00:11:34,393 --> 00:11:39,974
♪Old dreams flow like melodious poetry♪

129
00:11:39,974 --> 00:11:41,063
(Vast Mind, Eternal Will)

130
00:11:41,063 --> 00:11:44,338
♪Memories fade like the passing years♪

131
00:11:44,338 --> 00:11:46,970
♪The past events leave us confused♪

132
00:11:46,970 --> 00:11:53,290
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

133
00:11:54,874 --> 00:12:00,195
♪Ancient alleys guard time's secrets♪

134
00:12:00,762 --> 00:12:03,322
(Heaven and Earth Converge)

135
00:12:07,390 --> 00:12:10,330
(Virtue of Heaven and Earth)

136
