145
00:13:16,062 --> 00:13:20,826
♪Falling petals, endless longing♪

146
00:13:20,826 --> 00:13:23,162
♪Longing lingers within my heart♪

147
00:13:23,162 --> 00:13:29,862
♪Zither strings sigh
for the sorrow parting♪

148
00:13:29,862 --> 00:13:35,159
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

149
00:13:35,159 --> 00:13:37,279
Bow to Heaven and Earth.

150
00:13:37,279 --> 00:13:43,770
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

151
00:13:43,770 --> 00:13:48,154
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

152
00:13:48,154 --> 00:13:50,778
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

153
00:13:50,778 --> 00:13:55,679
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

154
00:13:55,679 --> 00:13:57,559
Bow to the parent.

155
00:13:57,559 --> 00:14:03,962
♪With nothing but memories left♪

156
00:14:15,759 --> 00:14:17,000
Good.

157
00:14:23,879 --> 00:14:26,039
Bow to each other.

158
00:14:35,960 --> 00:14:36,759
Wait!

159
00:14:47,559 --> 00:14:50,080
Who dares disrupt the wedding? Guards!

160
00:14:51,360 --> 00:14:53,679
This man isn't Gu Zhaoxi at all.

161
00:14:57,080 --> 00:14:58,440
I am the real Gu Zhaoxi.

162
00:14:59,360 --> 00:15:00,080
It was him.

163
00:15:01,039 --> 00:15:03,600
He ambushed me outside the city
and threw me into a wolf pit.

164
00:15:04,879 --> 00:15:07,360
He even used a sword
to disfigure my face.

165
00:15:21,480 --> 00:15:22,720
How terrifying!

166
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:23,879
What's going on?

167
00:15:23,879 --> 00:15:26,879
I knew he was treacherous,
but I never imagined

168
00:15:27,279 --> 00:15:29,399
he would go so far
as to steal my identity.

169
00:15:29,399 --> 00:15:30,679
Thrown into a wolf pit?

170
00:15:30,840 --> 00:15:33,279
Does the skeleton at the yamen
have something to do with them?

171
00:15:34,000 --> 00:15:35,879
How did he even survive?

172
00:15:36,159 --> 00:15:37,519
This Gu family is really...

173
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:39,240
My brother stands right here.

174
00:15:39,440 --> 00:15:41,279
Take this malicious troublemaker away!

175
00:15:41,480 --> 00:15:43,120
Hold on, Chaosheng.

176
00:15:43,399 --> 00:15:44,879
Why won't you let me finish?

177
00:15:49,799 --> 00:15:52,080
You claim to be Zhaoxi? Prove it.

178
00:15:52,399 --> 00:15:53,440
I can prove it!

179
00:16:00,679 --> 00:16:04,840
That day, we were both waiting
for my master's betrothed to return.

180
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:07,679
(Qi, Gu Zhaoxi's guard)
But he received a secret letter.

181
00:16:08,360 --> 00:16:10,000
(Despite my warnings, he left the city.)

182
00:16:15,000 --> 00:16:16,360
Who are you, sir?

183
00:16:17,159 --> 00:16:19,960
The one who asked you here.

184
00:16:21,720 --> 00:16:22,279
Get him.

185
00:16:25,639 --> 00:16:28,200
It was him! He kidnapped Master Zhaoxi!

186
00:16:28,799 --> 00:16:32,320
To rescue Master Zhaoxi,
I faked my death and followed them.

187
00:16:32,559 --> 00:16:35,360
I saw him destroy Master Zhaoxi's face

188
00:16:35,679 --> 00:16:37,080
and throw him into the wolf pit!

189
00:16:37,840 --> 00:16:41,360
If I hadn't saved Master Zhaoxi
while they were gone,

190
00:16:41,759 --> 00:16:42,679
who knows...

191
00:16:43,600 --> 00:16:47,480
I just never imagined
he could be so vicious and ruthless,

192
00:16:47,679 --> 00:16:50,200
trying to murder
Master Zhaoxi in that way.

193
00:16:51,200 --> 00:16:54,039
These past days, I've faced
death multiple times.

194
00:16:54,840 --> 00:16:59,159
But I held on just to keep this man
from bringing down my family.

195
00:17:00,799 --> 00:17:03,840
It's simple to prove my words.

196
00:17:04,319 --> 00:17:06,400
All these years, I've been
by Master Zhaoxi's side.

197
00:17:07,279 --> 00:17:10,319
Ask me any detail,
and everyone will know the truth.

198
00:17:12,279 --> 00:17:13,319
So it was really you?

199
00:17:14,240 --> 00:17:16,039
Qi has been by Zhaoxi's side
since childhood.

200
00:17:17,160 --> 00:17:18,559
I've long suspected you.

201
00:17:19,160 --> 00:17:20,640
What do you have to say now?

202
00:17:27,960 --> 00:17:31,440
Pity. We're just one step short
of completing the ceremony.

203
00:17:31,960 --> 00:17:35,720
Who are you? And why did you
come to the Gu family?

204
00:17:38,079 --> 00:17:41,079
Even now, you still
refuse to say anything?

205
00:17:41,640 --> 00:17:44,480
I have nothing to say.

206
00:18:04,880 --> 00:18:06,920
You've been deceiving me
from the very start.

207
00:18:07,519 --> 00:18:10,920
At Zuixian Building,
you deliberately got close to me.

208
00:18:11,720 --> 00:18:13,920
I gave you countless chances to explain,

209
00:18:14,519 --> 00:18:16,000
but you still wouldn't tell me.

210
00:18:20,880 --> 00:18:21,680
Dear.

211
00:18:23,799 --> 00:18:25,160
Do you truly refuse to believe me?

212
00:18:26,960 --> 00:18:27,680
Very well.

213
00:18:32,240 --> 00:18:33,799
This...

214
00:18:44,759 --> 00:18:45,359
Your Highness.

215
00:18:47,480 --> 00:18:48,160
Stand down.

216
00:18:51,119 --> 00:18:54,440
By my decree, no one is to harm her

217
00:18:56,480 --> 00:18:57,720
or the Gu family

218
00:18:59,839 --> 00:19:01,440
in any way.

219
00:19:02,000 --> 00:19:02,599
Your Highness.

220
00:19:02,759 --> 00:19:03,759
Do you hear me?

221
00:19:06,079 --> 00:19:06,640
Yes.

222
00:19:22,106 --> 00:19:25,178
(Virtue of Heaven and Earth)

223
00:19:30,319 --> 00:19:32,400
When will the frost and snow return?

224
00:19:34,799 --> 00:19:36,079
May we meet again

225
00:19:38,200 --> 00:19:39,519
when spirits return.

226
00:19:42,400 --> 00:19:43,160
Your Highness.

227
00:19:49,759 --> 00:19:50,720
Let's go.

